						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Āditya II. Year 3: A.D. 959.</hi></p>						

						<p>Mutilated. Registers a tax free grant of 3 <hi rend="italic">vēlis</hi> of land and house sites to Kāri Puliyaṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Chōḻamārāyaṉ of Paḻuvūr in Kuṉṟa-kūṟṟam and his 12 servants <hi rend="italic">(kavarippiṇākar)</hi> for performing some services in the temple of Śrī Mahākāḷam, by Nirañjana Paṇḍitar and other authorities of the temple.</p>						

